Selenium grid is the concept which will allow you to run your test on multiple browser and machines
Selenium grid will allow us to run the test on multiple nodes which will reduce the total execution
time which is the main adv of test automation

To understand Selenium Grid there are 2 new concepts

1) Hub : Hub is the central machine which will redirect the commands to the respective node based on parameters
2) Node : Node is an actual machine where the test will be executed 